Live Demo: https://vimeo.com/936424964/d2ff6bb0f3?share=copy

The feature works as expected and picking up most of the words that were spoken. 
However, there is a slight lag when the words are spoken and some of the words
were not selected because of the wrong word being understood. There should be some
feature that speeds up the response and accuracy of the words being selected, 
or a guess that most resembles the word.